The patches from from two hibernate bug reports:
https://hibernate.onjira.com/browse/HHH-1803
https://hibernate.onjira.com/browse/HHH-1283

Go into this directory:
hibernate-orm/hibernate-core

First apply this patch:
patch -p3 < fetch-scroll-collection-3.5.4.patch.txt

Then go into this directory:
hibernate-orm/hibernate-core/src/main/java

Then apply this patch:
patch -p5 < ~/hibernate-orm/criteria-scroll-fetch-collection.patch.txt
